  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba 3 \u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 hour power cut tomorrow too",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Ratnayake, chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, said today (21) afternoon that due to the lack of sufficient fuel and water for electricity generation, power cuts were allowed for 3 hours tomorrow (22).",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Ratnayake said that electricity will be cut for 1 hour and 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour and 20 minutes during the night in the 20 zones up to CityW.",
        "That power cut was allowed for 2 hours and 30 minutes from 6.00 am to 8.30 am for Colombo cities and AITCC category, and for 3 hours from 5.00 am to 8.00 am for M, N, O, X, Y and Z zones. Chairman of the Public Utilities Commission Mr. Janaka Ratnayake said further."
      ],
